{"tid":2029574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"吹奏上街冇用論 美國唔幫論既柒頭皮應該要穿越返去1937年","createTime":"2020-05-22T09:49:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T15:09:30.000Z","uid":212731,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"40dd39b617d8971920daab7c0bbbaac7694ec9be","tid":2029574,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:49:15.000Z","msg":"咁支那就唔會畀共產黨竊國<br />\n香港都唔會咁慘<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adfa00d00de040092de101a25ccdaa658659ccfd","tid":2029574,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T09:54:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>屌</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>你</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>老</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>母</strong></span></div>"},{"pid":"a9e10fe9660f0e8f45dfbf2a4ab530043ecc543f","tid":2029574,"uid":212731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033b0a344f6a658a006fd874cd2e6d4158adaad3","tid":2029574,"uid":212731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"1937年嗰陣 美國一直行緊孤立主義 冇人覺得美國人會出兵捲入二戰<br />\n日本有航母大和號零式<br />\n國民黨有幾百萬兵力 但武器全部廢既 共產黨二萬五千里大逃亡完黎 淨返一千人都冇 窮到得對草鞋<br />\n<br />\n投降派都認為日本肯撚定可以統領大東亞<br />\n最後幾多人估到幾年之後美國真係出兵打柒德國同日本? <br />\n又有幾多人估到當年得對草鞋既共產黨可以竊到成個中國?<br />\n<br />\n如果連登仔係共產黨員就好 瘋狂吹奏抗日冇用 聯蘇冇用<br />\n依家香港唔使咁慘"}]}